ponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"PinceCodeInputComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"pin code input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Pin code input"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of dimensions (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"OrangeThemePinCodeInputComponentTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Something which provides all semantic tokens of _"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/alldimensionsemantictokensprovider","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract14TokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"TokensProvider"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic09DimensionB6TokensP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"DimensionSemanticTokens"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider","title":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"}}}